conds between sets.</p><p class="tiptap-paragraph"></p><p class="tiptap-paragraph">⚡ <strong><u>Finisher (REPS & SETS)</u></strong></p><ul class="tiptap-bullet-list"><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">3 {{exercise:0705:side bridge v. 2}} (controlled, mindful core engagement)</p></li><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">3 {{exercise:1604:world greatest stretch}} (focus on lower abs)</p></li><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">3 {{exercise:forearm-plank:Forearm Plank}} (strong, stable hold)</p></li></ul><p class="tiptap-paragraph">Rest 45-60 seconds between sets.</p><p class="tiptap-paragraph"></p><p class="tiptap-paragraph">🧘 <strong><u>Cool Down 10'</u></strong></p><ul class="tiptap-bullet-list"><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph"><strong>Static Stretching (8 min):</strong> 60 {{exercise:pigeon-stretch:Pigeon Stretch}} , 30 sec per side seated glute stretch, 60 sec seated wide angle pose sequence</p></li><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph"><strong>Diaphragmatic Breathing (2 min):</strong> Lie supine, one hand on chest, one on belly. Slow inhale through nose (belly rises), slow exhale through mouth. Focus on calming nervous system, slowing heart rate.</p></li></ul>$mobility_repair$, updated_at = now() where id = 'WOD-MS-B-1778653804864';
