ing mechanics. Rest 60 seconds between sets.</p></li><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">{{exercise:0705:side bridge v. 2}}– 3 sets x 8 reps, focusing on glute and hamstring activation, and controlled spinal extension. Rest 60 seconds between sets.</p></li></ul><p class="tiptap-paragraph"></p><p class="tiptap-paragraph">⚡ <strong><u>Finisher</u></strong></p><ul class="tiptap-bullet-list"><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">{{exercise:0003:air bike}} 15</p></li><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">{{exercise:1604:world greatest stretch}} 10</p></li><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">{{exercise:bird-dog:Bird Dog}}</p></li></ul><p class="tiptap-paragraph">Complete 3 rounds:</p><p class="tiptap-paragraph"></p><p class="tiptap-paragraph">🧘 <strong><u>Cool Down 5'</u></strong></p><ul class="tiptap-bullet-list"><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">russian twist – 30 seconds each side</p></li></ul>$mobility_repair$, updated_at = now() where id = 'WOD-MS-B-1766026160083';
