-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">{{exercise:1011:band seated twist}} x 12 reps per arm, 2-1-2-0 tempo, 60s rest)</p></li></ul><p class="tiptap-paragraph"></p><p class="tiptap-paragraph">⚡ <strong><u>Finisher (For Time)</u></strong></p><ul class="tiptap-bullet-list"><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">{{exercise:0003:air bike}}</p></li><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">{{exercise:1604:world greatest stretch}}</p></li></ul><p class="tiptap-paragraph"></p><p class="tiptap-paragraph">🧘 <strong><u>Cool Down</u></strong></p><ul class="tiptap-bullet-list"><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">{{exercise:cat-cow-stretch:Cat-Cow Stretch}}</p></li><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">{{exercise:pigeon-stretch:Pigeon Stretch}}</p></li><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">{{exercise:1511:hamstring stretch}}</p></li><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">{{exercise:0817:triceps stretch}}</p></li><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">{{exercise:1167:dynamic chest stretch (male)}}</p></li></ul>$mobility_repair$, updated_at = now() where id = 'FREE-beg-mobility-stability-E-1776661814230';
