tap-bullet-list"><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">{{exercise:1419:iron cross stretch}} - 1 set x 30s hold per side</p></li><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">{{exercise:1587:seated wide angle pose sequence}} - 1 set x 45s hold</p></li><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">{{exercise:1363:spine stretch}} - 1 set x 30s hold</p></li></ul>$mobility_repair$, updated_at = now() where id = 'FREE-mobility-stability-B-1776659291363';
