strong><u>Finisher (10-minute AMRAP)</u></strong></p><ul class="tiptap-bullet-list"><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">{{exercise:0979:band horizontal pallof press}}-15 reps per side</p></li><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">{{exercise:3645:single leg bridge with outstretched leg}}-10 reps per leg</p></li></ul><p class="tiptap-paragraph"></p><p class="tiptap-paragraph">🧘 <strong><u>Cool Down</u></strong></p><ul class="tiptap-bullet-list"><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">{{exercise:1511:hamstring stretch}}</p></li><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">{{exercise:1713:assisted prone lying quads stretch}}</p></li><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">{{exercise:cat-cow-stretch:Cat-Cow Stretch}}</p></li></ul></div>$mobility_repair$, updated_at = now() where id = 'FREE-int-mobility-stability-E-1777866830241';
