rm)</u></strong></p><ul class="tiptap-bullet-list"><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">{{exercise:0805:suspended abdominal fallout}} - 2 sets x AMRAP with perfect form (focus on full extension and retraction, rest 60s)</p></li></ul><p class="tiptap-paragraph"></p><p class="tiptap-paragraph">🧘 <strong><u>Cool Down</u></strong></p><ul class="tiptap-bullet-list"><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">{{exercise:1419:iron cross stretch}} - 2 minutes per side (slow, deep breathing)</p></li><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">{{exercise:1366:upward facing dog}} - 2 minutes (hold and breathe)</p></li><li class="tiptap-list-item"><p class="tiptap-paragraph">{{exercise:cat-cow-stretch:Cat-Cow Stretch}} - 2 minutes (synchronized with breath)</p></li></ul></div>$mobility_repair$, updated_at = now() where id = 'PREM-adv-mobility-stability-E-1777870092016';
